<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boaz_Huss" title="Boaz Huss">Boaz Huss</a>, professor of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kabbalah" title="Kabbalah">Kabbalah</a> at <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ben-Gurion_University_of_the_Negev" title="Ben-Gurion University of the Negev">Ben-Gurion University of the Negev</a></li>
<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ron_Kaplan" title="Ron Kaplan">Ron Kaplan</a> (born 1970), Olympic gymnast</li>
