<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Naccache" title="David Naccache">David Naccache</a> (born 1967), cryptologist, professor at France's Ecole normale supérieure</li>
<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Newman_(political_geographer)" title="David Newman (political geographer)">David Newman</a>, professor and Dean of Social Science and Humanities, BGU</li>
<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ilan_Ramon" title="Ilan Ramon">Ilan Ramon</a>, Israel's first astronaut; died in the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Space_Shuttle_Columbia_disaster" title="Space Shuttle Columbia disaster">Columbia disaster</a></li>
