<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bouak%C3%A9" title="Bouaké">Bouaké</a>, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ivory_Coast" title="Ivory Coast">Ivory Coast</a><sup id="cite_ref-138" class="reference"><a href="Beersheba#cite_note-138">&#91;135&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>
